   - `[\w\u4e00-\u9fa5]+`: Matches one or more word characters (alphanumeric and underscore) or Chinese characters.
   - `[\w\u4e00-\u9fa5.-]*`: Matches zero or more word characters, Chinese characters, dots, or hyphens.
   - `@`: Matches the '@' symbol.
   - `[\w\u4e00-\u9fa5]+`: Matches one or more word characters or Chinese characters in the domain part.
   - `(?:\.[\w\u4e00-\u9fa5]+)*`: Matches zero or more occurrences of a dot followed by one or more word characters or Chinese characters.

